This paper deals with social choice mechanisms, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves decision-making under uncertainty, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of metrics and the analysis of distortion are related to topics in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves mathematical optimization and analysis, which is a topic in mathematical aspects of computer science (cs.MA).
